WORLD-CLASS AMENITIES & UNSURPASSED PRIVILEGES
Exclusive Membership
Fisher Island Club is South Florida’s most exclusive golf and private club.
As a member of the Fisher Island Club, your privileges include access to a premier Miami golf course, racquet club, casual & fine dining restaurants, spa, salon & wellness center, marinas, private beach club, the Vanderbilt Mansion pool, a kids’ club and the exclusive member events. Whether you seek relaxation or excitement, club membership opens the door to a wealth of world-class amenities & services to satisfy your every want and need. For additional information, please click below.
MEMBERSHIP INQUIRY

EQUITY MEMBERSHIP
Your Subtitle Goes Here

Equity Membership is available to Fisher Island property owners. Membership includes privileges for primary member, spouses, and dependent children under the age of 24. Each Equity Membership represents an equity ownership in the Club.
EQUITY MEMBERSHIP BENEFITS INCLUDE:
Preferred member dues
Snooker Club privileges
Preferred golf fees, preferred marina rates
Priority reservations for golf, tennis, spa, and beach cabanas
Unlimited complimentary tennis privileges
Each Equity Membership represents an equity ownership in the Club
Equity Members may opt to include golf privileges for the additional annual fee. Greens fees and cart fees for golf apply.
OPTIONAL ANNUAL GOLF MEMBERSHIP
Golf Privileges Include:
No greens fees for unlimited play
Unlimited range use
Complimentary golf clinics. Cart fees for golf apply
PRIVILEGES INCLUDE ACCESS TO:
Private Beach and Beach Club
Snooker Club
Theapolis
Beach Club
Sunset Bar
Porto Cervo
La Trattoria
Greenside
Island Market
Aviary with exotic birds
The Links P. B. Dye-designed, 9-hole golf course
Tennis Center: 17 tennis courts, incl. 2 grass, 3 hard (Deco Cushion), 5 European-style red clay, and 7 Har-Tru clay, plus 4 pickleball courts
Spa Internazionale, Fitness Center & Salone di Bellezza
Two Deep-water Marinas
Observatory
Member Events
Family Activities
For information on Equity Membership, please call
305-535-6076
or email
membership@fisherislandclub.com
